      <scopecontent id="aspace_113b2cd8b7173d4202abe2c19cecd458">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs documenting the construction of Jonathan Edwards College at Yale. Included are some photographs of the construction of Dickinson and Wheelock Halls, which were incorporated into Jonathan Edwards College in 1932. Also included are interior and exterior views of courtyards, common rooms, and dining hall.</p>
      </scopecontent>
